{"tid":1692492,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[區選] 含淚同賣港之間，我選擇反枱","createTime":"2019-11-04T06:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T16:28:58.000Z","uid":137721,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8cb6a5ab7eb379aefe71e05ec49b3554ceab866e","tid":1692492,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:01:41.000Z","msg":"區選臨近，大家都有個想法就係<strong>代議士不代表我</strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>當中普遍既論調都係:</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: gold;\">制度抗爭根本已經失效投黎都無用</span> / 制度內外都要抗爭唔通唔做？<br />\n- <span style=\"color: gold;\">寧願投建制唔投熱狗</span>/ 選入去只係為左cut佢地資源<br />\n- <span style=\"color: gold;\">成班選入去都係食人血饅頭</span> / 都好過益左班建制派<br />\n- <span style=\"color: gold;\">隨時換左個票箱你都唔知啦</span> / 唔可以咁陰謀論，可以消耗人手監察<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>事實:</strong></ins><br />\n現行制度下選舉制度已經完全腐朽，選出黎既代議士不乏內奸及無能之士，無辦法真實反映民意。<br />\n<br />\n投票只因無得選擇，並非因為我想選你。<br />\n<br />\n而大家亦太低估港共政權使橫手既程度，將區選諗得太理想。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在此想大家討論一樣野: <strong>取消區選有咩問題？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>核心價值</ins></strong>: 反映政制不公不義，推翻政制而並非杯葛，取消制度內抗爭，停止俾假希望大家<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>點做</ins></strong>: 612你可以圍立法會阻止二讀，聽日你可以圍票站阻礙投票流程<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>留意</strong></ins>: 取消區選既唔可以係燃燒彈，而係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>催淚彈</strong></span>"},{"pid":"466854387992ed394502a522da188e98b1b40d8b","tid":1692492,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:06:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2337f4039ab83cb3dc5b2533391143eca17c505","tid":1692492,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:09:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1229051de6916fc5e4a27c05bae71f764277a0b8","tid":1692492,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:12:53.000Z","msg":"不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d686bebcf404f563424af3681732cc1c36595eae","tid":1692492,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:38:27.000Z","msg":"熱狗含淚投票撚淨係識負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a534e4d885359d3f3db931b4c6332a0eaba09a3","tid":1692492,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:28:58.000Z","msg":"樓主你駁得晒其他人講果d point point先再講<br />\n<br />\n區議會選舉係一場贏輸都有得分，點都照抗爭既副本<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675467</a>"}]}